data.description: Amazing move in ready home with master on the ground floor, huge loft plus three bedrooms upstairs, and everything brand new.  Brand new carpet, tile, and two tone paint through out.  Huge private grassy backyard on corner lot with RV gate for all your toys makes this the perfect home.  Please show and sell.
